Flame-Palette version 0.02
==========================

This module provides facilities to create and manipulate palette
files, usually used in fractal flames created by flam3.

It is written in pure perl and just needs Perl itself and the modules
listed below "DEPENDENCIES".

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Math::Interpolator::Linear
  XML::Parser
  XML::Writer

